flowchart TD
    subgraph ING["DATA INGESTION — cached, never live during demo"]
        A1["OpenAQ — 3 CPCB stations
        (RK Puram · Anand Vihar · Punjabi Bagh)
        121K+ measurements, 91 days"]
        A2["Open-Meteo Weather
        Temperature · Humidity · Pressure
        Wind speed/direction"]
    end

    A1 --> FS
    A2 --> FS

    FS[("FEATURE STORE — SQLite
    81 features per row:
    lags (t-1h to t-72h),
    rolling averages (6h/24h/72h),
    calendar features (hour/dow/month/stubble season),
    weather (temperature/humidity/pressure/wind)
    **NO satellite features**")]

    FS --> MODEL["FORECASTING MODEL — LightGBM
    × 3 independent models (24h / 48h / 72h)
    RMSE: 33.5 / 35.5 / 35.9
    Beats persistence at all horizons
    Benchmarked vs persistence + seasonal-naive baselines"]

    MODEL --> IDW["IDW SPATIAL INTERPOLATION
    3 station points -> 70 AC centroids
    Distance-based confidence tiering:
    HIGH (<5km): 19 ACs
    MEDIUM (5-15km): 46 ACs
    LOW (>15km): 5 ACs
    Low ACs get explicit honesty caveat in all output"]

    IDW --> AGENT["ADVISORY & Q&A AGENT
    Groq · Llama 3.1 8B Instant (0.3-0.9s)
    EN + Hindi bilingual
    Grounded in real feature importances ONLY
    Explicitly constrained: never reference satellite/fire
    Low-confidence: mandatory honesty caveat
    Fallback: pre-generated cached responses for demo safety"]

    IDW --> API["FASTAPI BACKEND — 4 endpoints
    GET /forecast/{horizon} -> GeoJSON
    GET /forecast/{unit_id}/{horizon}
    POST /advisory/{unit_id}/{horizon} -> EN+Hindi
    POST /qa/{unit_id} -> grounded answer
    StaticFiles: serves frontend
    Port: 7860 (HF Spaces standard)"]

    AGENT --> FE
    API --> FE

    FE["LEAFLET FRONTEND — HTML5 + JS
    Dark CartoDB basemap
    CPCB official color scale
    Confidence-tier border encoding:
    · High: solid green border
    · Medium: dashed amber border
    · Low: thick red border + crosshatch overlay
    Time slider: Today / +24h / +48h / +72h
    Unit click -> advisory panel (EN+Hindi)
    Q&A box with example chips
    AQI range legend
    Fallback: pre-cached responses for Groq failures"]

    FE --> DEPLOY["HUGGINGFACE SPACES
    Docker · Single container
    Python 3.11-slim
    Backend + Static Frontend
    Secrets: GROQ_API_KEY (never committed)
    URL: rohitdecodes-vayudrishti.hf.space"]
